com.ai.ASTCells

Class ARefASTCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ai.ASTCells.AbstractASTCell
      • com.ai.ASTCells.ARefASTCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTCell

    public class ARefASTCell
extends AbstractASTCell
    Used to represent an Array reference. Takes in an internal or external symbolASTCell, along with some form of expression Cell to represent the index of the given symbol.

    #_exp must be either an internal or external symbol cell

    _index must have a non-null number value

    Distinguishes between internal and external inputs to reference in VM data types.

    Author:
    Martin Tice
